---

---

<section class="py-20 px-6 bg-section-bg">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto mb-16">
    <span class="text-[#6352ff] text-base mb-4 block font-mono uppercase tracking-widest">// Tarifs</span>
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-black uppercase text-title leading-tight mb-4">Des offres taillées<br>pour l'excellence.</h2>
    <p class="text-title/50 text-sm max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">Chaque projet est unique. Ces formules constituent une base de travail.<br> Je suis à votre écoute pour un devis sur-mesure.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto items-start">
    <!-- Card Vitrine -->
    <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-[32px] p-10 border border-title/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-4 transition-all duration-500 flex flex-col   justify-between h-full">
      <div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-8 border-b border-title/5 pb-8">
          <div>
            <span class="uppercase text-[10px] font-black tracking-widest text-[#6352ff] bg-[#6352ff]/5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Essentiel</span>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-black uppercase text-title mt-4">Site Vitrine</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="text-right">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-5xl font-black text-title italic">1200</span>
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#6352ff] ml-1">€</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[10px] uppercase font-bold text-title/20">à partir de</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-title/50 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-10">
          Idéal pour les artisans, indépendants et TPE souhaitant une présence en ligne élégante, performante et crédible.
        </p>

        <ul class="space-y-5 mb-12 font-bold">
          <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-title/80">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#6352ff] mr-4"></div>
            Design unique & 100% sur-mesure
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-title/80">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#6352ff] mr-4"></div>
            Optimisation SEO
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-title/80">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#6352ff] mr-4"></div>
            Interface Responsive (Mobile, Tablette)
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-title/80">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#6352ff] mr-4"></div>
            Animations fluides & interactives
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-title/80">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#6352ff] mr-4"></div>
            Hébergement & Domaine (1 an inclus)
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <a href="#contact" class="w-full py-5 rounded-2xl bg-title text-white text-center text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-[#6352ff] transition-all duration-300 transform group-hover:scale-[1.02]">
        Démarrer mon projet
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Card E-Commerce -->
    <div class="group relative bg-title rounded-[32px] p-10 border border-white/10 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-4 transition-all duration-500 flex flex-col justify-between h-full transform md:scale-105">
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-10 -translate-y-1/2 bg-[#6352ff] text-white text-[10px] font-black px-5 py-2 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest shadow-lg">
        Le plus demandé
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-8 border-b border-white/10 pb-8">
          <div>
            <span class="uppercase text-[10px] font-black tracking-widest text-white/50 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">E-Commerce</span>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-black uppercase text-white mt-4">Boutique</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="text-right">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-5xl font-black text-white italic">3500</span>
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#6352ff] ml-1">€</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[10px] uppercase font-bold text-white/30">à partir de</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-10">
          Pour les marques prêtes à vendre en ligne avec une expérience d'achat fluide, sécurisée et optimisée pour la conversion.
        </p>

        <ul class="space-y-5 mb-12">
          <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-white">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#6352ff] mr-4 shadow-lg shadow-[#6352ff]/50"></div>
            Tout inclus dans l'offre Vitrine
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-white">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#6352ff] mr-4 shadow-lg shadow-[#6352ff]/50"></div>
            Plateforme E-commerce
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-white">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#6352ff] mr-4 shadow-lg shadow-[#6352ff]/50"></div>
            Gestion des produits & stocks (illimités)
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-white">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#6352ff] mr-4 shadow-lg shadow-[#6352ff]/50"></div>
            Paiement sécurisé (stripe & paypal)
          </li>
            <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-white">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#6352ff] mr-4 shadow-lg shadow-[#6352ff]/50"></div>
            Formation à la gestion de la boutique
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <a href="#contact" class="w-full py-5 rounded-2xl bg-[#6352ff] text-white text-center text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white hover:text-title transition-all duration-300 transform group-hover:scale-[1.02] shadow-lg shadow-[#6352ff]/30">
        Lancer ma boutique
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="text-center mt-10">
    <p class="text-title/50 text-sm">Besoin d'une offre sur-mesure ? <a class="text-[#6352ff]/90">Parlons de votre projet</a></p>
  </div>
</section>